* 2.1.2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sat Nov  3 2012
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- suport KRISPException on oop mode

Fri Nov  2 2012
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- support PHP 5.4
	- OOP suport KRISP::(__construct,search,searchEx,close,mtimeInterval,debug)


* 2.1.1
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mon Feb 27 2012
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- release 2.1.1
	- changed header value with krisp-config --cppflags on config.m4
	- fixed libkrisp link error
	- fixed wrong internal api type


* 2.1.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sat Sep 11 2010
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- release 2.1.0
	- linked over libkrisp 3.1.x
	- add krisp_set_mtime_interval function
	- add krisp_set_debug function
	- changed interanl api to krisp_format_convert


* 2.0.2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mon Sep  6 2010
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- support over php 5.3
	- fixed build error that undeclare 'second_arg_force_ref'
	- chagend deprecated zend_get_parameters_ex to zend_parse_parameters
	- remove global extension variable api for compat with 5.1


* 2.0.1
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mon Aug  9 2010
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- linked with over libkrisp 3.0.2
	- removed unused geoip variables
	- fix license to LGPL current and old versions


* 2.0.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sat Jul  3 2010
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- changed krisp_long2prefix to krisp_mask2prefix
	- changed krisp_prefix2long to krisp_prefix2mask

Fri Jul  1 2010
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- enhanced build environment

Fri Jun 18 2010
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- changed link libkrisp library version. require over libkrisp 3.0.0
	- add new function
	  krisp_search_ex
	  krisp_netmask
	  krisp_network
	  krisp_broadcast
	  krisp_prefix2long
	  krisp_long2prefix


* 1.2.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Wed Nov 29 2006
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- support userdb and changed hostip database usage

Sun Nov 26 2006
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- support hostip database
	- if krisp_open hasn't any arguments, database file set default KRISP database
	- required over libkrisp 2.1.0


* 1.1.3
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Fri Oct 13 2006
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- changed memory allocation to malloc from emalloc when krisp_open


* 1.1.2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Thu Sep 14 2006
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- add second argument in kr_open function
	  array : key
	          (string) geocity => whether search GeoIPCity database. default 0
	          (string) dopen   => GeoIP database open type.
	          (string) iopen   => GeoIPISP database open type.
	          (string) copen   => GeoIPCity database open type.


* 1.1.1
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sat Sep  9 2006
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- fixed wrong use of GeoIP link


* 1.1.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Thu Sep  7 2006
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- update 1.1.0
	- required over libkrisp 2.0.0
	  if you have libkrisp 1.x, then use mod_krisp 1.0.x
	- support several geoip extensions
	  support GeoIPCity (if you have database)
	  support GeoIPISP (if you have database)


